    <stitle>Spanish - Gu&#237;a para Localizaci&#243;n de Fallas del Sistema El&#233;ctrico - 3200, 4200, 4300, 4400,
        7300, 7400, 7500, 8500, 8600 - FRONT DRIVE AXLE: SPICER S-9000 - INNER AND OUTER AXLE SHAFT DISASSEMBLY
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="disassemble" graphiccount="2">
        <title>INNER AND OUTER AXLE SHAFT DISASSEMBLY</title>
        <para>Use
            <hotlnk document="s02009_27.xml" xrefid="f0200975">Figure 75</hotlnk>
            as a reference to disassemble inner and outer axle shafts.
        </para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">To separate inner and outer axle shafts, first remove all of the bearing cap retaining rings
                (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0200980">Figure 80</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f0200980" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g0200980" filename="../figg02/G0200980.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 80. Remove Bearing Cap Retaining Rings</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Press out U-joint bearing caps and remove cross. Inspect U-joint bearing caps and cross and
                replace if necessary (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f0200981">Figure 81</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f0200981" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g0200981" filename="../figg02/G0200981.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 81. Inspect U-Joint Bearing Caps</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
